{"article_id":"Bq3g6DqdfubIpCkL","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"The day","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"the House submitted articles of impeachment against President Donald Trump to the Senate ,","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"a Ukraine-born associate of Trump ' s lawyer said","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"that \" President Trump knew exactly what was going on '' in Ukraine during the White House 's alleged pressure campaign at the center of Trump 's upcoming trial .","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"Lev Parnas ,","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"who is alleged to have assisted in the pressure campaign ,","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"Trump and Giuliani were routinely informed of the behind-the-scenes developments in the work","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"he did on their behalf in Ukraine .","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"\" He was aware of all my movements .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"I would n't do anything","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"without the consent of Rudy Giuliani , or the president .","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"I have no intent ,","depth":13},{"id":14,"text":"I have no reason","depth":13},{"id":15,"text":"to speak to any of these officials , \"","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"Parnas told MSNBC ' s Rachel Maddow in an interview .","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"White House press secretary Stephanie Grisham pushed back on Parnas ' statements .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"`` These allegations are being made by a man","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"who is currently out on bail for federal crimes","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"and is desperate to reduce his exposure to prison , ''","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"she said of Parnas ,","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"who is facing unrelated campaign finance charges .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"`` The facts haven ' t changed","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"- the president did nothing wrong","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"and this impeachment ,","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"which was manufactured and carried out by the Democrats","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"has been a sham from the start . ''","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"More :","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Rudy Giuliani associate","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"Lev Parnas battles","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"to stay out of jail ,","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"cites Ukraine 'threats '","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"In an interview with the New York Times , Parnas said","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"he did not speak to Trump directly about his efforts ,","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"though he said","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"he met the president on several occasions .","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"But Giuliani told him","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"he was keeping Trump updated ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"Parnas said .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"Giuliani told the Times","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"that Parnas was `` a proven liar ''","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"who was seeking attention .","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"The former New York mayor said","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"it was `` sad to watch how the Trump haters are using '' Parnas .","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"House Democrats impeached Trump for abuse of power and obstruction of Congress","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"for allegedly withholding military aid and a White House visit","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"in order to pressure Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky to investigate former Vice President Joe Biden and a conspiracy theory about the 2016 election .","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"Parnas said Wednesday","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"that the desired investigation into Biden `` was never about corruption ''","depth":15},{"id":50,"text":"as the Trump administration and his allies on Capitol Hill have claimed .","depth":15},{"id":51,"text":"`` It was strictly about Burisma","depth":15},{"id":52,"text":"which included Hunter Biden and Joe Biden , \"","depth":15},{"id":53,"text":"he said .","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"The `` main objective '' was to get the government of Ukraine to announce the investigation into Biden ,","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"Parnas said .","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"That echoed the testimony of U.S . Ambassador to the European Union Gordon Sondland ,","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"who said","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"what mattered to Trump was the public announcement of the investigations , not the investigations themselves .","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"\" He had to announce the investigations .","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"He did n't actually have to do them , ''","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"Sondland told the House Intelligence Committee on Nov. 20 .","depth":13},{"id":62,"text":"In another interview , Parnas told CNN 's Anderson Cooper","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"that only the press releases from Ukraine mattered","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"`` because nobody actually trusted them to do an investigation . ''","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"`` It was all about 2020 ,","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"to make sure","depth":15},{"id":67,"text":"he had another four years , ''","depth":15},{"id":68,"text":"Parnas said .","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"`` That was the most important thing","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"is for him to stay on another four years","depth":15},{"id":71,"text":"and keep the fight going .","depth":15},{"id":72,"text":"I mean ,","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"there was no other reason","depth":15},{"id":74,"text":"for doing it . ''","depth":15},{"id":75,"text":"The former Giuliani associate said","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"he was willing to testify about his allegations in the Senate impeachment trial .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"In his interview with Cooper , Parnas described two occasions","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"in which he offered a `` quid pro quo '' to Ukrainian officials ,","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"though he said","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"those were not the only times .","depth":14},{"id":81,"text":"In the first , he said","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"he delivered a message to former Ukrainian President Petro Poroshenko","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"that Trump would grant him a White House visit , or at least statement of support ,","depth":15},{"id":84,"text":"if he announced the opening of the investigations .","depth":15},{"id":85,"text":"After Zelensky was elected ,","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"Parnas said","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"a demonstration of U.S. support at his inauguration was a top priority for the new president .","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"Parnas said","depth":16},{"id":89,"text":"he told Zelensky in `` very strict and very stern '' terms","depth":17},{"id":90,"text":"that he had to immediately announce the `` Biden investigation ''","depth":18},{"id":91,"text":"if he wanted anything from Trump .","depth":18},{"id":92,"text":"`` If they did n't make the announcement ,","depth":17},{"id":93,"text":"basically there would be no relationship , ''","depth":17},{"id":94,"text":"Parnas said .","depth":16},{"id":95,"text":"He said","depth":16},{"id":96,"text":"the threat implied","depth":17},{"id":97,"text":"that not just military aid , but all assistance , would be cut off","depth":18},{"id":98,"text":"if Zelensky did not cooperate .","depth":18},{"id":99,"text":"In addition , Vice President Mike Pence would `` not be at the inauguration","depth":17},{"id":100,"text":"and there would be no visit to the White House . ''","depth":17},{"id":101,"text":"When he was told it did not look like the announcement was coming ,","depth":18},{"id":102,"text":"Giuliani said ,","depth":19},{"id":103,"text":"`` OK , they 'll see , ''","depth":19},{"id":104,"text":"according to Parnas .","depth":17},{"id":105,"text":"Parnas also worked with Giuliani","depth":15},{"id":106,"text":"to try and secure a U.S. visa for a former Ukrainian prosecutor","depth":16},{"id":107,"text":"who said","depth":17},{"id":108,"text":"he had incriminating information about Biden ,","depth":17},{"id":109,"text":"according to text messages","depth":15},{"id":110,"text":"Parnas ' attorney gave to House investigators .","depth":15},{"id":111,"text":"Parnas and another associate of Giuliani , Igor Fruman , are facing unrelated campaign finance charges","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"and evidence in the case includes $ 325,000","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"allegedly contributed under a false donor name to a political action committee for Trump .","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"New impeachment evidence :","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"Lev Parnas , associate of Trump lawyer Rudy Giuliani , pressed for Ukraine investigation into Joe Biden","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"Previously , Trump denied","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"knowing the two Ukrainian-born business partners","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"when asked ,","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"dismissing a photograph","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"that showed him with one of the men at the White House .","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"Trump has also denied","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"he did anything wrong in regards to Ukraine","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"and has dismissed the impeachment investigation as a `` witch hunt '' .","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"\" I don ' t know those gentlemen , \"","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"Trump told reporters on the South Lawn of the White House in October .","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"The interview with Parnas comes","depth":6},{"id":127,"text":"after House Democrats released new records and evidence from him ,","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"including a photograph of a previously-undisclosed letter from Giuliani to Ukrane President Volodymyr Zelensky on May 10 .","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"\" In my capacity as personal counsel to President Trump and with his knowledge and consent , I request a meeting with you on this upcoming Monday , May 13th , or Tuesday , May 14th , \"","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"Giuliani wrote .","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"Parnas continued in the interview ,","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"`` I mean","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"they have no reason","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"to speak to me .","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"Why would President Zelenskiy ' s inner circle , or Minister Avakov , or all these people , or President Poroshenko meet with me ?","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"Who am I ?","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"They were told to meet with me .","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"And that 's the secret","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"that they 're trying to keep . ''","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"`` I was on the ground","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"doing their work , \"","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"he declared ,","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"later saying","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"Giuliani told officials in Ukraine","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"that Parnas was a representative of Trump","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"and acting on his behalf .","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"Parnas said","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"that he would put Giuliani on speakerphone","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"so the president 's personal lawyer would confirm","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"Parnas was representing Trump .","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"More :","depth":7},{"id":152,"text":"Was former Ambassador Yovanovitch being watched in Ukraine ?","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"She wants that investigated","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"following new evidence","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"Parnas also claimed","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"former national security adviser John Bolton ,","depth":11},{"id":157,"text":"who has said","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"he will testify","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"if subpoenaed by the Senate ,","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"Attorney General William Barr and Rep. Devin Nunes , R-Calif. , were involved or aware of what was happening .","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"Phone records show","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"that Nunes , the ranking Republican on the House Intelligence Committee and one of Trump 's most outspoken supporters in Congress , spoke with Parnas in April .","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"Nunes told Fox News on Wednesday","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"that he did not know Parnas","depth":13},{"id":165,"text":"and did not recognize the name","depth":14},{"id":166,"text":"when he called .","depth":14},{"id":167,"text":"But he said","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"he remembered that call ,","depth":13},{"id":169,"text":"which was `` very odd , random","depth":14},{"id":170,"text":"and talked about random things . ''","depth":14},{"id":171,"text":"`` This is someone","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"who 's been indicted for major felonies , ''","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"Nunes said .","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"`` This is someone","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"who does n't tell the truth . ''","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"Parnas told CNN","depth":10},{"id":177,"text":"that Pence and acting White House Chief of Staff Mick Mulvaney were also aware of the `` quid pro quo . ''","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"When asked how he knew","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"that Pence was aware of the alleged plan","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"to pressure Zelensky ,","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"Parnas cited","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"his close relationship with Giuliani .","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"`` Democrat witnesses have testified under oath in direct contradiction to Lev Parnas statements last night , ''","depth":10},{"id":184,"text":"said Pence 's Chief of Staff Marc Short in a statement .","depth":10},{"id":185,"text":"`` This is very simple :","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"Lev Parnas is under a multi-count indictment","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"and will say anything to anybody","depth":13},{"id":188,"text":"who will listen","depth":13},{"id":189,"text":"in hopes","depth":13},{"id":190,"text":"of staying out of prison . ''","depth":13},{"id":191,"text":"More :","depth":5},{"id":192,"text":"House sends impeachment of President Trump to Senate for trial ,","depth":6},{"id":193,"text":"names 7 'managers '","depth":7},{"id":194,"text":"to prosecute case","depth":7},{"id":195,"text":"Parnas and Maddow also discussed screenshots of WhatsApp messages with Republican candidate for Congress Robert Hyde","depth":6},{"id":196,"text":"that were released by House Democrats .","depth":6},{"id":197,"text":"The two appear to discuss surveillance of former Ambassador to Ukraine Marie Yovanovitch ,","depth":7},{"id":198,"text":"who was ousted by the Trump administration ,","depth":8},{"id":199,"text":"while she was in Ukraine .","depth":8},{"id":200,"text":"Parnas claimed","depth":8},{"id":201,"text":"that `` there was no other motivation ''","depth":9},{"id":202,"text":"to remove Yovanovitch","depth":10},{"id":203,"text":"except to get her out of the way of the pressure campaign .","depth":10},{"id":204,"text":"He also stated","depth":8},{"id":205,"text":"he met Hyde at a Trump Hotel","depth":9},{"id":206,"text":"where Hyde was often `` at the bar ''","depth":10},{"id":207,"text":"intoxicated .","depth":10},{"id":208,"text":"Contributing :","depth":2},{"id":209,"text":"Bart Jansen , Nicholas Wu , Kevin McCoy , Jeanine Santucci","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":419,"left":417,"right":418,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":417,"left":0,"right":416,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":416,"left":399,"right":415,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":399,"left":334,"right":398,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":334,"left":236,"right":333,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":236,"left":225,"right":235,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":225,"left":213,"right":224,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":213,"left":211,"right":212,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":211,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution",